name: Green Tiles Tote/Diaper Bag

-everyday wear
-computer bag

-diaper bag

name: Wet Bag Faux Leather
description:
Carry baby's diapers and necessities in style with this beautiful wet bag. It is made out of heavy duty marine vinyl and lined with a waterproof PUL fabric. This clutch can easily hold several diapers and wipes and measures at 10" x 9" x 2" (gusset).

This bag has a nice leather look and so versatile to use. Here are some ideas:

-snacks
-wet swimsuits/clothing
-cosmetics and toiletry
-iPad Generation 2 or similar (this will be lined with the cotton fabric)

It is perfect for outings and date nights with the fabric lining option. The lining is a pretty and fun grey and white polka dot 100% cotton print.

***Please specify at checkout whether you would like a waterproof or cotton lining. If no choice is specified, I will make the wet bag with the waterproof lining.***

Marine Vinyl is an excellent choice since it is mildew resistant, waterproof and cleans easily with a damp cloth.

*********************************************************************************************************

This item is made to order. Please specify PUL or fabric lining. Allow 2 weeks for shipping.
